OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773778273
OL,3,CBritish Airways cancels flights to
OL,4,CDubai and other Middle East hubs until
OL,5,CJune
OL,7,FBritish Airways (BA) has paused the
OL,8,Fmajority of its flights to parts of
OL,9,Fthe Middle East until at least June as
OL,10,FIranian strikes on the Gulf region
OL,11,Fcontinue.
OL,13,FAll flights to Amman, Bahrain, Dubai,
OL,14,Fand Tel Aviv are temporarily cancelled
OL,15,Funtil May 31, while flights to Doha
OL,16,Fare suspended until April 30, and will
OL,17,Fresume with a limited schedule planned
OL,18,Funtil June. Abu Dhabi flights remain
OL,19,Fcancelled until October.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
