CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773778273
OL,3,CBritish Airways cancels flights to
OL,4,CDubai and other Middle East hubs until
OL,5,CJune
OL,7,FThe airline industry is facing its
OL,8,Fmost challenging time since the Covid
OL,9,Fpandemic after Israel and the US
OL,10,Flaunched attacks on Iran, with Tehran
OL,11,Fretaliating with strikes on its Gulf
OL,12,Fneighbours and Israel that shut down
OL,13,Fairspace in the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773778273
OL,3,CBritish Airways cancels flights to
OL,4,CDubai and other Middle East hubs until
OL,5,CJune
OL,7,FWhile airspace has reopened, the
OL,8,Fsituation is uncertain, with Iran
OL,9,Fcontinuing to strike key
OL,10,Finfrastructure sites of US allies
OL,11,Facross the Middle East. UAE airspace
OL,12,Fwas shut overnight due to a drone
OL,13,Fattack on a fuel storage tank, causing
OL,14,Ffresh flight disruption.
OL,16,FA drone attack temporarily closed
OL,17,FDubai airport on Monday. Firefighters
OL,18,Fbattled the flames for several hours,
OL,19,Fforcing the world's busiest
OL,20,Finternational airport to suspend
OL,21,Fflights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
