FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773778273
OL,3,CBritish Airways cancels flights to
OL,4,CDubai and other Middle East hubs until
OL,5,CJune
OL,7,FBA's services to Riyadh and Jeddah are
OL,8,Fcontinuing to operate as planned and
OL,9,Fcustomers booked onto any of these
OL,10,Froutes can change their flights until
OL,11,FMay 31.
OL,13,FThe UK Foreign Office is warning
OL,14,FBritish citizens against all but
OL,15,Fessential travel to Bahrain, Kuwait,
OL,16,FQatar and the United Arab Emirates
OL,17,F(UAE).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
