PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773778273
OL,3,CBritish Airways cancels flights to
OL,4,CDubai and other Middle East hubs until
OL,5,CJune
OL,7,FIn a statement, British Airways said:
OL,8,F"Due to the continuing uncertainty of
OL,9,Fthe situation in the Middle East and
OL,10,Fairspace instability, and to provide
OL,11,Fmore clarity to our customers, we've
OL,12,Fextended the temporary reduction in
OL,13,Four flying schedule in the region.
OL,15,F"We're keeping the situation under
OL,16,Fconstant review and are directly in
OL,17,Ftouch with affected customers to offer
OL,18,Fthem a range of options.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
