PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773778273
OL,3,CBritish Airways cancels flights to
OL,4,CDubai and other Middle East hubs until
OL,5,CJune
OL,7,F"Since the situation in the Middle
OL,8,FEast began, we've helped thousands of
OL,9,Fcustomers return home and operated
OL,10,Feight relief flights from Muscat in
OL,11,FOman. We are also operating additional
OL,12,Fflights to and from Singapore (x4) and
OL,13,FBangkok (x3), and continue to review
OL,14,Foptions to bring back more customers
OL,15,Fwho have been disrupted."
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
